State *: Mandatory Field; Must be a valid state for selected Country
Latitude: non mandatory; Must be a valid Latitude value
Longitude: non mandatory; Must be a valid Longitude value
Account Type *: Mandatory Field; Should be one of your existing account types
Status *: Set status to TRUE to ensure Client is active; Must be TRUE or FALSE
Contact First Name: Max 100 chars; If empty all other contact fields are ignored
Main Contact *: Mandatory Field; Must be TRUE or FALSE
column31: If you need to import data for custom fields specify the name of custom field in column header. Remove column if there are no custom fields.
